Total and Autofast recently launched their partnership at Madaraka Total service station, Nairobi. Speaking during the event, Total Kenya MD Olagoke Aluko said, “This partnership is a demonstration of Total’s desire to continuously offer motorists value for money while guaranteeing quality. The partnership allows Total to offer motorists quality parts from the Original Equipment Manufacturers, resulting in significant savings in time, cost and increased car lifespan.” These car care services will be available at the Madaraka, Ngong Road, Karen and Muthaiga Total service stations.